m <- GetAssayData(x, assay="ADT", slot="data")

d_KO <- d |> filter(background == "KO_spleen")

d_WT <- d_WT |> mutate(stage=case_when(
  CD27 >= 0.5 & CD11B < 0.28 ~ "R1",
